text: Hornbach is a German DIY-store chain offering home improvement and do-it- yourself goods. The company was founded in 1977. It is headquartered in Bornheim (Pfalz), Germany. == Other websites == * Official website Category:1970s establishments in Germany Category:1977 establishments in Europe Category:Rhineland-Palatinate Category:Retail companies of Germany
